               <note>Fiey provides the following bibliographic citations: <quote source="#bibl51-1">Differentes biographies : BHO, 1060-64. Ses reuvres : Barsaum, Lu 'lu '2 , 296-312. Sa vie, ses ecrits, sa doctrine : DTC, XIV, col. 1988-2000 (G. Bardy). BSO, II, 1015-16 (J. Rabbi).</quote>
